name: QQQmix
description:
NAI free......?

This model was only merged with the model considered not to contain NAI

If the model I used includes NAI, please let me know

Setting

Items not listed are defaults

You may change the setting to your liking

▼t2i setting

  • Sampling method : DPM ++ 2M SDE Karras

  • Sampling steps : 30

  • CFG scale : 13 (Use CFG scale modification and set it higher)

  • Clip Skip : 2

Enable Dynamic Thresholding (CFG Scale Fix)

  • Mimic CFG Scale : 7

  • Top percentile of latents to clamp : 95

  • Mimic Scale Scheduler : Harf Cosine Up

  • CFG Scale Scheduler : Harf Cosine Up

  • Minimum value of the CFG Scale Scheduler : 3.5

▼i2i setting

Denoising strength : 0.3

ControlNet

  • Preprocessor : tile_colorfix+sharp

  • Control Weight : 0.5

  • Ending Control Step : 0.45

  • Sharpness : As you wish

Tiled Diffusion

  • Upscaler : 4×AnimeSharp

Tiled VAE

  • Encoder Tile Size : 1280
